title: Dr. Sanjay Gupta / Performing Emergency Brain Surgery
description: Find out why Sean is wearing a foot boot and hear Dr. Wali explain the connection between a peanut allergy and a lung transplant. Dr. Sanjay Gupta talks about his double life in medicine and as a public figure. And don’t miss his story of performing emergency life saving brain surgery with a Black & Decker drill.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
